urdu transliteration text:
Karbala yeh bata mera bhaiyya kaha hai gaya Zuljana aagaya roke zainab ne tha yun kaha
Zainab said crying when Zuljana returned
@HujjatELC

Chadaare chin gayi aal ki Zahra saani ko qaid kiyaAa Bhi de natawaan ke gale tauq zaalim ne pehna diya,be pala unth thay aur kumba Muhammad ka tha
Zahra's daughter has been made captive,
@HujjatELC

Jab tha kufa ke bazaar mei kafila qaidion ka gaya X2Kufiyon ne sitam ye kiya patharo kani barsa diya,baalon ko kohl kar liya zainab ne Parda bana
The Kufans committed atrocities by throwing stones,
@HujjatELC
